com.jogamp.gluegen

Interface GlueEmitter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CStructAnnotationProcessor.AnnotationProcessorJavaStructEmitter, DebugEmitter, JavaEmitter, ProcAddressEmitter

    public interface GlueEmitter
    Specifies the interface by which GlueGen requests glue code to be generated. Can be replaced to generate glue code for other languages and foreign function interfaces.

      • emitStruct

        void emitStruct(CompoundType t,
              Type typedefType)
                throws Exception
        Emit glue code for the given CompoundType. typedefType is provided when the CompoundType (e.g. "struct foo_t") has not been typedefed to anything but the type of "pointer to struct foo_t" has (e.g. "typedef struct foo_t {} *Foo"); in this case typedefType would be set to pointer type Foo.

        Exception
